  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/b54b0898516e7fc1758fe5be3970dfd2.poster.avif?t=1761912586\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/b54b0898516e7fc1758fe5be3970dfd2.webm?t=1761912586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/b54b0898516e7fc1758fe5be3970dfd2.mp4?t=1761912586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>What happens when you combine <i>suffering</i>, <i>agony</i> and <i>shame</i>? You get <strong>PAIN</strong>, of course!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/bdb901143f2a20764544c0680d94029e.poster.avif?t=1761912586\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/bdb901143f2a20764544c0680d94029e.webm?t=1761912586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/bdb901143f2a20764544c0680d94029e.mp4?t=1761912586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is PAIN, you might wonder?</h2>PAIN is a concoction of <u>EVERYTHING EVIL</u> the common human mind can think of. You can also see it as a successful <u>psychological experiment</u>, being able to leave many nerves rekt.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/8ac9fce1e3b4761c8701a44bfcb74d5d.apng?t=1761912586\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/8ac9fce1e3b4761c8701a44bfcb74d5d.poster.avif?t=1761912586\" class=\"bb_img\" width=576 height=324 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What are PAIN's promises?</h2><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Extreme space-physics</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Unforgiving and annoying gimmicks</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">NO checkpoints (imagine lol)</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Timing tomfoolery</ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.apng?t=1761912586\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.poster.avif?t=1761912586\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.apng?t=1761912586\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.poster.avif?t=1761912586\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.apng?t=1761912586\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.poster.avif?t=1761912586\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.apng?t=1761912586\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205420/extras/32e6caff32052549b7a1a4be2a53e978.poster.avif?t=1761912586\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why was it created?</h2><u>No one knows.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb